1
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,840
The truth is, when it comes to

2
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,360
Peach Blossom Town,

3
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,320
we're both outsiders here.

4
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:41,080
We came to get a piece of the pie.

5
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,760
If we can, we'll stick around a few years.

6
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,320
And if we can't,

7
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,800
we just turn around and leave.

8
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,200
We came here just to make some money.

9
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,680
Is that so?

10
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,480
I remember a saying I really like.

11
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,720
It's the law of the jungle.

12
00:01:57,520 --> 00:02:00,680
Either you're at the table, or you're on the menu.

13
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:02,640
Let me put it bluntly.

14
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,240
Today, you're sitting and I'm standing,

15
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,560
so I speak to you with the utmost respect.

16
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,440
But if one day our positions were reversed,

17
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:15,080
with me sitting and you standing,

18
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:18,560
you'd have to speak respectfully to me.

19
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,920
I just worry you'd have a bitter feeling.

20
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,920
That you couldn't quite accept it.

21
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,840
So I sincerely hope you rise up the ranks.

22
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,480
Thanks for your kindness, President Zhang.

23
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,000
I'll certainly do it as soon as I can.

24
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:50,720
Then I'll look forward to your good news.

25
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,040
Hello?

26
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,200
Lawyer Qin.

27
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,520
It's about the patent squatting again.

28
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:45,840
In the emails I sent to the Chairman,

29
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:49,200
there's detailed discussion of the designs,

30
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,840
and the designer himself is mentioned too,

31
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:54,360
and of course, the send dates as well.

32
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:57,480
Could these serve as evidence?

33
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,280
The send dates are before the registration.

34
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,240
Yes.

35
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,720
Two months earlier, in fact.

36
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,960
The whole process is crystal clear.

37
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,800
If so, then there's no problem.

38
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,760
The emails can serve as direct evidence.

39
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,200
Alright, Lawyer Qin.

40
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,480
Thank you.

41
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,400
Let's meet up once we're back in Shenzhen.

42
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,279
Xin Ran.

43
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,440
Go ahead.

44
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:18,880
There's one more thing,

45
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,519
a crucial issue I need to warn you about.

46
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:25,200
I went to Lin Family Village this morning.

47
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,680
They've built dragon boats for centuries,

48
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,800
but know nothing about paper dragon boats.

49
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:38,920
Xuan Yan's paper dragon boat is out too.

50
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,640
I've already spoken with Secretary Peng.

51
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,640
Today we'll issue

52
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:48,080
a notice that the paper boat won't race.

53
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,360
The Song of Farewell is cancelled too.

54
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,800
Let's minimize the impact as best we can.

55
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,480
Even if the paper dragon boat fails,

56
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,320
no need to cancel the Song of Farewell.

57
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,880
You planned it for so long,

58
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,240
and did so much research.

59
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:03,200
The paper dragon boat is the centerpiece.

60
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,880
The Song of Farewell

61
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,720
was meant to promote the paper boat.

62
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:13,080
Without the paper dragon boat finale,

63
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,200
what's the point of the Song of Farewell?

64
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:20,520
The main thing is, after Xuan Yan's mess,

65
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:26,160
Peach Blossom Town has lost its spirit.

66
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:30,280
No one wants to take part anymore.

67
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,480
But Director,

68
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,200
you put so much effort into it.

69
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,640
You even recreated Li Bai's "To Wang Lun".

70
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,000
Such a great idea,

71
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,480
it's such a shame to give it up like this.

72
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,760
I'm sorry, Director Liao.

73
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,560
It's not me I feel sorry for.

74
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,480
I feel sorry for

75
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,440
those hundreds of thousands of fans.

76
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:04,680
And Secretary Peng failed the county.

77
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:27,880
Bro Min, stop tallying it up.

78
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,560
I took a rough look at it.

79
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:32,440
All of this adds up to a lot of money.

80
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,920
I say we forget about the raw materials.

81
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,360
Everyone can just figure it out.

82
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,240
Exactly.

83
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,240
That won't be necessary.

84
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,360
I'll say it again, same as before.

85
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,560
For anyone who wants out,

86
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,880
and any materials or equipment to sell,

87
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:47,600
give it all to me.

88
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,440
I know you mean well for us.

89
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,120
But this is no small sum.

90
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,600
You can't shoulder this all alone.

91
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,360
Small sum or not, that's my problem.

92
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:58,760
Worst case, I'll throw in the factory.

93
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:03,080
If that's not enough, I'll throw in my house too.

94
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,880
And if that still isn't enough,

95
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,600
then I'll take out a loan.

96
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:11,560
Bottom line, I've got this covered.

97
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,800
Come on, look at yourself.

98
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,320
The way you're talking,

99
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,720
you make it sound like we're forcing you.

100
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:19,680
We're all only human, you know.

101
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:22,160
Ignore all that uproar the last few days.

102
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,600
All that cursing heaven and earth,

103
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,840
it's just that we can't afford the losses.

104
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,960
It stings.

105
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:29,320
A capable person, when hitting hard times,

106
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,600
won't just sit around blaming everyone.

107
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:33,080
Instead, they'll figure out a way.

108
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,800
Xuan Yan is exactly that kind of person.

109
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,720
Why did I dare take over this mess?

110
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,360
It's because I put my faith in Xuan Yan.

111
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,800
I put my faith in Cultural and Creative.

112
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,240
You don't believe it, huh?

113
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,800
None of you believe it, huh?

114
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:52,400
Fine, then let's make a bet.

115
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,080
Let's see who ends up regretting it.

116
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:28,800
Come on.

117
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:30,440
No need.

118
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:30,800
Let's go.

119
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,560
It's fine, it's fine.

120
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,520
I can manage.

121
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,440
Come on.

122
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,679
Why did you stop?

123
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,000
We've reached the top.

124
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,800
There's no path left.

125
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,600
When there's no path, just stop.

126
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:03,720
Focus on the task right in front of you.

127
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,600
That's actually a path in itself.

128
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:09,520
I don't get it. What are you saying?

129
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,320
What's so hard to understand?

130
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,560
Today, just focus on getting

131
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,080
today's task done well.

132
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,680
And tomorrow, do whatever needs doing.

133
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:23,320
It's not you who's in trouble.

134
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,120
So what do you call this?

135
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:27,600
They call this "easy for you to say."

136
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,640
But you're sitting now, too.

137
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,560
This place really is the best.

138
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:38,800
The moment I come here, my heart calms down.

139
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:40,560
Of course it does.

140
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:43,240
This is the very root of the Xuan family.

141
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:47,160
For thousands of years, the Xuan ancestors

142
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,960
all started right here,

143
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,920
step by step,

144
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:53,600
completing all 108 steps.

145
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:56,640
Well-tempered, through fire and water,

146
00:09:57,000 --> 00:10:00,680
after countless trials, made one fine sheet.

147
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,520
Xuan Yan, you shouldn't be staying here.

148
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:09,160
You should go do what you're meant to do.

149
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,320
You mean

150
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,400
I should be like them,

151
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:20,160
starting all over from scratch here?

152
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:23,240
You can't make paper here anyway.

153
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,640
What I mean is,

154
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,880
return to your Cultural and Creative work.

155
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,120
Xuan Bao'er was stolen by someone else.

156
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,880
So what? Just start over from scratch.

157
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,240
Easy for you to say.

158
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,200
Xuan Bao'er and Paper Fairy,

159
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:43,240
the time and effort I poured in

160
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:45,240
before the market finally accepted them.

161
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,720
Wanting to start all over again,

162
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,760
that's hard.

163
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,840
You just feel

164
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,800
you can't design anything better than Xuan Bao'er.

165
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,480
But Xuan Bao'er isn't actually the best.

166
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:01,240
To dig deeper,

167
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,840
it's that you lack the willpower.

168
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:04,520
You haven't been tempered enough.

169
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:08,640
You lack the courage to rise from the ashes.

170
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,360
The Sixth Precept of the Xuan Family:

171
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:14,720
Bark and straw, through a thousand trials

172
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:18,280
and weathering the seasons, shed their rawness to gain a core of jade.

173
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:22,160
To live in this world, one must purify the heart,

174
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:25,400
temper the body, discard the false to find the true,

175
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,600
and thus achieve integrity.

176
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:27,960
To make paper

177
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,400
is to make yourself.

178
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:35,320
If the Pteroceltis bark doesn't endure

179
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,880
the pain of being slashed, boiled, and stripped,

180
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:39,640
it can't become jade-white Xuan paper.

181
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,640
People are really no different.

182
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,720
Once you break through this trial,

183
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:47,440
you'll create better Cultural and Creative work.

184
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,960
I know now why I failed.

185
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,520
I miss Master.

186
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:17,040
Once you decide when to leave, let me know ahead of time.

187
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:19,160
Bring two bottles of good wine to Master for me.

188
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:47,280
Thanks.

189
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,080
Leaving already?

190
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:51,880
I'm off.

191
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,760
Take the... take the carrying pole with you!

192
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,080
Do it yourself.

193
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:12,120
At this point, all I can do is apologize.

194
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,760
Everyone's hopes for the paper boat,

195
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:16,160
after all, were something we stirred up.

196
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,360
And now...

197
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,360
this is all we can do.

198
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,720
I hope everyone can forgive us.

199
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,840
The Song of Farewell hasn't even begun,

200
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,320
and already we've run into this.

201
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:30,400
I worry it'll hurt the whole show later.

202
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:35,400
On Xuan Yan's behalf, I apologize to you.

203
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:36,880
Don't be like that.

204
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:38,440
These past couple of days,

205
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:41,240
I've been apologizing to the higher-ups.

206
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:44,120
Thankfully, everyone's been understanding.

207
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:47,560
But I still hope Xuan Yan comes back soon.

208
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:50,760
Our brilliant young man of Peach Blossom Town

209
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,520
can't be knocked down by a small thing.

210
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:54,440
I...

211
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,680
Xuan Yan!

212
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,520
Hurry, answer it!

213
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:00,760
Hello?

214
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:08,520
It's Xuan Yan!

215
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:08,800
Let's go!

216
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,240
Yes, yes, it's him, it's him!

217
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:10,960
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

218
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:11,840
Xuan Yan!

219
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:12,760
President Xiao!

220
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:13,400
Xuan Yan!

221
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:14,640
Xuan Yan is back!

222
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:15,920
Xuan Yan!

223
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:16,760
Xuan Yan is back!

224
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:17,920
Where did you run off to?

225
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:18,640
You're finally back!

226
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:19,760
Where have you been all these days?

227
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,520
We've all been looking for you.

228
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,040
We searched for you for so many days.

229
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:24,640
Where's Bro Min?

230
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:25,880
President Xiao is over there.

231
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:26,520
President Xiao is over there.

232
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:27,880
You're finally back!

233
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:28,840
He's inside.

234
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:29,680
President Xiao!

235
00:14:29,680 --> 00:14:30,280
President!

236
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:30,760
It's been several days now.

237
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:31,360
Xuan Yan is back!

238
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,080
Where did you go?

239
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,720
Do you know how many people looked for you?

240
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:35,480
Bro Min.

241
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:36,960
As long as you're back, that's what matters.

242
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:42,480
I see.

243
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,400
First, I owe everyone an apology.

244
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,280
I'm sorry.

245
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:48,760
Come on, what good does an apology do?

246
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,000
Why did you run off?

247
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,520
I didn't run, and I never intended to.

248
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:56,640
After all, this whole mess started with me.

249
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,560
We've hit such a huge setback.

250
00:14:58,640 --> 00:14:59,880
How do we move forward from here?

251
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,440
I owe everyone an explanation.

252
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:02,920
It's just that I hadn't figured out

253
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:04,120
how to face all of you.

254
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,760
Now I've thought it through.

255
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:08,000
Face what must be faced, handle what must be handled.

256
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:10,360
This road, we've got to keep walking it.

257
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:12,040
Alright, then, tell us.

258
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:13,520
What do we do next?

259
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,520
Two options.

260
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,640
One, compensation.

261
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:19,120
Whatever you lost, I'll pay back.

262
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:21,280
What I can pay now, I'll pay now.

263
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,360
What I can't pay yet,

264
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:23,800
I'll write you an IOU first.

265
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:26,080
I'll pay you back slowly once I earn it.

266
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:27,320
Until this debt is paid,

267
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:29,040
I'll never leave Peach Blossom Town.

268
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,280
You don't need to worry about this.

269
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:33,760
Xuan Yan.

270
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,360
President Xiao just said

271
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:38,760
anyone who wants to quit the Cooperative,

272
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:40,480
he'll bear it all himself.

273
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:41,000
Yeah.

274
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:42,960
Right.

275
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:46,640
Bro Min.

276
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:47,760
Now for the second option.

277
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:51,880
I'm going to start over,

278
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:54,640
and keep making Xuan paper Cultural and Creative products.

279
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,440
Keep making them?

280
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:58,280
The ones pulled and discontinued before,

281
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,080
they're all in the past now.

282
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,120
Let's not bring them up again.

283
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:02,360
And let me make this clear to everyone.

284
00:16:02,680 --> 00:16:05,120
I've ended the contract with Dayazhai.

285
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,200
Going forward,

286
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:09,520
as the leader of the Cooperative,

287
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:10,760
I'll throw everything I have

288
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:13,160
into designing and developing new products.

289
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,360
Please trust me.

290
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:17,200
I'll definitely create even better works.

291
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:20,640
Then we'll apply for our own patents,

292
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,360
and win back the market.

293
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,640
Can this really work? I wonder.

294
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:26,080
I think this can work, honestly.

295
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,400
Of course,

296
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:30,880
the road to success is bound to be hard.

297
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:33,480
To be reborn, one must first endure the flames.

298
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,160
If any of you don't want to continue,

299
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,400
I won't stop you.

300
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:38,320
Like I said,

301
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:40,480
whatever I owe, I'll pay back.

302
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:42,520
But if anyone's willing to trust me,

303
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,760
to believe in me, Xuan Yan,

304
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:46,560
and keep going with the Cooperative,

305
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:49,520
we'll get through this tough time together.

306
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:50,520
I will,

307
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:53,120
I will lead you out of this crisis.

308
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,000
And what rightfully belongs to us,

309
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:57,040
we'll take back into our own hands.

310
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:00,760
I'm in with you.

311
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:05,040
For no other reason

312
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,119
than that you're standing here,

313
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:09,960
and for what you just said.

314
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:13,960
We're all bosses here.

315
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:17,359
Whose business is smooth from the start?

316
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:21,280
Who hasn't hit a few bumps along the way?

317
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:22,960
Afraid of losing?

318
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:26,640
Getting back up and going on isn't losing.

319
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:30,200
Xuan Yan could take a little notebook

320
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:31,360
and turn it into something huge.

321
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,760
He designed a few little dolls

322
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,160
that made Dayazhai's Zheng Guohui jealous.

323
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:38,280
And who is Zheng Guohui?

324
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,160
He runs a big business.

325
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:42,360
If even he got jealous, what does that tell you?

326
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,960
It tells you Xuan Yan has real ability.

327
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:45,480
It tells you Xuan Yan has talent.

328
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,960
So I firmly believe,

329
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,400
as long as I stick with you,

330
00:17:53,120 --> 00:17:54,480
we're bound to do something big.

331
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:58,480
I'm in too.

332
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,360
This might not be the right time to say this,

333
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:06,880
but I want everyone to know

334
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:10,240
that the town's desire to serve you,

335
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:12,920
to help you grow and live better lives,

336
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:13,640
will never change.

337
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:14,960
We're not afraid to fail,

338
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,760
nor afraid of your criticism.

339
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:19,160
But as long as we get this right,

340
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:21,600
as long as Peach Blossom Town's Xuan paper

341
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:22,880
Cultural and Creative industry can thrive,

342
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,160
and revive the traditional Xuan paper industry,

343
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,960
then I think it's all worth it.

344
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:28,600
I'm in too.

345
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,160
Me? I don't know anything about business.

346
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:32,880
And I don't believe

347
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,440
I could ever amount to much on my own.

348
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:38,440
But I trust them. I trust Xuan Yan.

349
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:42,120
I trust Director Lin. I trust President Xiao.

350
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:43,000
I'm in.

351
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:43,960
Great!

352
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:46,400
It's not about the bread, it's about the pride.

353
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:48,200
With all these entrepreneurs in Peach Blossom Town,

354
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,560
whoever chickens out,

355
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,680
that's who's not a real man.

356
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:51,800
Right, I'm in!

357
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:54,320
Xuan Yan and President Xiao have gone all in.

358
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:56,160
What have small fry like us got to fear?

359
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:56,760
I'm in!

360
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:59,520
With enough guts, you can pull the emperor off his horse.

361
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,440
We're doing this!

362
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:03,240
Let's go head to head with Dayazhai.

363
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:03,720
I'm in!

364
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,240
I'm in, all the way!

365
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:05,760
Let's just do it!

366
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:06,440
Right, I'm in!

367
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,040
Great!

368
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,360
Then let's do it right now.

369
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:10,520
Let's sign new contracts.

370
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:11,840
Yes, yes, yes!

371
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:13,400
Come on, let's go sign the contracts.

372
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,720
Let's go.

373
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:15,480
Great!

374
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:16,240
Go sign the contracts.

375
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,680
Come on, let's go sign the contracts.

376
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:18,280
Come on, come on.

377
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:26,480
Sister Xin, I've got great news for you.

378
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,840
Xuan Yan and the others are back.

379
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:30,000
Their Cooperative is up and running again.

380
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:33,400
I knew he could do it.

381
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:35,920
So now, signing the contract

382
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,680
shouldn't feel like such a burden, right?

383
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:42,040
The latest intel from Shenzhen:

384
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:45,200
the Chairman suspects you and is furious.

385
00:19:45,520 --> 00:19:46,760
If you don't sign now,

386
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:47,960
you may never get the chance.

387
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:49,920
The Chairman guessed right.

388
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,160
I'm going to make a different choice.

389
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:55,520
Maybe we should be like them,

390
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:57,080
no big deal,

391
00:19:57,520 --> 00:19:58,280
and start over from scratch.

392
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:03,000
President Xin,

393
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,720
you're an experienced woman.

394
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,520
Don't be a fool like Xuan Yan.

395
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:10,400
You've got to look forward.

396
00:20:12,520 --> 00:20:13,800
I know what you're trying to do.

397
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,160
All I can say is, I'm sorry,

398
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,560
but your plan is going to fall through.

399
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:22,480
President Xin,

400
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:27,680
here are two Sales commission contracts

401
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,760
that need your signature.

402
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:31,040
Okay.

403
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:40,920
Here.

404
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:42,600
Thank you, Sister Xin.

405
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,440
You tampered with my emails.

406
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:47,920
Yes.

407
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,000
Those emails between you and the Chairman,

408
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:50,960
I deleted them all.

409
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:53,960
I did it for your own good.

410
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:56,320
Of course,

411
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,440
I admit it was for my own good too.

412
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,800
I love Southern Anhui.

413
00:21:01,120 --> 00:21:03,240
I stayed here after I graduated from college.

414
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,720
You know that.

415
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,800
I even bought a house in the county town.

416
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:12,680
I trained you myself, from the ground up.

417
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,320
Why would you do this?

418
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,640
If you'd handed those emails to Xuan Yan,

419
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:22,000
the Chairman would fire us in a heartbeat.

420
00:21:22,560 --> 00:21:24,320
I think what you did was really foolish.

421
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:27,480
I won't make such a pointless sacrifice.

422
00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:30,800
I just want to protect myself.

423
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:36,600
I did nothing wrong.

424
00:21:38,760 --> 00:21:40,120
Protecting yourself isn't wrong.

425
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:47,800
Betraying your conscience is what's wrong.

426
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:17,760
Invoke the Dragon Head!

427
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:38,080
The rest is up to you now.

428
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:41,160
The Paper Dragon Boat has to shine.

429
00:23:59,040 --> 00:23:59,680
Master

430
00:24:05,080 --> 00:24:05,600
Master

431
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:08,640
Master

432
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:10,840
Why did you fall asleep out here?

433
00:24:10,840 --> 00:24:11,760
You'll catch a cold.

434
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,800
What brings you here?

435
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:15,280
I came to check on you.

436
00:24:17,520 --> 00:24:17,920
Good.

437
00:24:19,280 --> 00:24:20,560
You didn't have to bring anything.

438
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,400
Is something the matter?

439
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:28,760
Xuan Yan is back.

440
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:30,920
Everything's been sorted out.

441
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:33,800
Everyone believes in Xuan Yan's abilities.

442
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:36,240
So they've decided to keep investing.

443
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:37,600
The cooperative will carry on.

444
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,200
I see.

445
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:47,040
There's one more thing.

446
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:50,240
What is it?

447
00:24:55,080 --> 00:24:56,240
You're a grown man now.

448
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:59,680
Spit it out. Why so Plagued by fears?

449
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:03,320
I... I wanted to ask you a favor.

450
00:25:03,520 --> 00:25:04,480
I was afraid you'd say no.

451
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,560
Go on.

452
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:08,240
The Dragon Boat Race is coming up soon, right?

453
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:11,000
Xuan Yan's building his paper dragon boat.

454
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:14,520
But we can't just sit idle. We need to train.

455
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:17,320
The strokes, the rhythm, all of it.

456
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:19,080
We really can't skip the practice.

457
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,320
After all, this time...

458
00:25:21,560 --> 00:25:23,760
we represent the Peach Blossom Town Xuan Paper team.

459
00:25:24,520 --> 00:25:25,640
If we don't do well...

460
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:27,920
won't we shame all us paper folk?

461
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,400
Right, right, exactly.

462
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:31,000
If we really lost the race...

463
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:35,280
that'd be like making a fool of ourselves,

464
00:25:37,040 --> 00:25:37,840
utterly shameful, wouldn't it?

465
00:25:37,840 --> 00:25:38,560
Exactly.

466
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:41,840
So we'd like you to come out of retirement.

467
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:44,120
Me?

468
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,480
Look at the state I'm in.

469
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:49,200
Can I even row a dragon boat?

470
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:50,560
Master.

471
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,360
Even if you had all the strength in the world,

472
00:25:52,520 --> 00:25:54,520
we'd never let you do the rowing.

473
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:57,280
You're the face of our town's Xuan paper.

474
00:25:57,840 --> 00:26:00,760
So we want you to be our Helmsman.

475
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:05,200
But the paper dragon boat isn't finished.

476
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,000
How can we practice?

477
00:26:06,320 --> 00:26:07,520
There's no time to lose.

478
00:26:07,560 --> 00:26:08,920
We'll find another dragon boat to train with first.

479
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:10,920
I've already got everyone lined up.

480
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:12,920
Now we're just waiting on you.

481
00:26:17,840 --> 00:26:18,400
Master.

482
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:20,760
The Helmsman's seat...

483
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:23,720
if you don't take it, no one else dares to.

484
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,680
Stop chasing these unreliable schemes.

485
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:29,320
All right?

486
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,960
If it flops, you'll be a laughingstock.

487
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,160
Okay, okay.

488
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:35,080
As long as you're at the helm,

489
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:36,800
we're sure to nail it.

490
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:38,840
So you're saying yes?

491
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:44,400
Thank you so much, Master, thank you!

492
00:26:44,600 --> 00:26:45,680
I'll go get things ready right away.

493
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:47,240
Let's meet at Peach Blossom Pond this afternoon.

494
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:47,720
No, no.

495
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:49,680
Your Madam has already made lunch.

496
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:50,760
Stay here and eat.

497
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:54,000
Just mentioning Madam's cooking, I really miss it.

498
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,080
Steamed Pork with Rice Flour.

499
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:56,600
My mouth's already watering.

500
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,280
Then stay and eat here.

501
00:26:58,280 --> 00:26:58,800
No, no, no.

502
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:00,200
I'm afraid if I eat...

503
00:27:00,320 --> 00:27:02,600
a full belly might mess up my performance.

504
00:27:03,800 --> 00:27:05,080
It's fine, go on and eat.

505
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:06,240
See you this afternoon.

506
00:27:06,320 --> 00:27:07,000
See you at Peach Blossom Pond this afternoon.

507
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:07,240
Okay.

508
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:08,240
All right, Master, I'll be off then.

509
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:20,800
Come on, come on

510
00:27:20,800 --> 00:27:21,760
Come on, come on

511
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:22,760
Come on, come on

512
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:24,400
Hold it up and compare, go on

513
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:25,440
Compare it, compare it

514
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:28,240
Look at your beard

515
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:30,640
And you, hold a cup in your hand

516
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:33,280
See, now it looks just right, doesn't it?

517
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,920
Look how much it resembles it!

518
00:27:37,600 --> 00:27:39,040
Now that's got the vibe

519
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:40,680
Take a picture of me, Taozi

520
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,040
I didn't bring my phone

521
00:27:42,280 --> 00:27:43,000
I didn't bring mine either

522
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:43,760
A phone, a phone

523
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:44,480
Got one, got one

524
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:46,760
You're all dressed up already

525
00:27:48,760 --> 00:27:49,560
Old Liao

526
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:51,280
What's going on here, Old Liao?

527
00:27:51,280 --> 00:27:51,760
Secretary Peng, Secretary Chen

528
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:53,400
Dressed up this early already

529
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:54,080
Well, you see

530
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:56,680
Who has time to change when we're so busy?

531
00:27:57,320 --> 00:27:58,960
Old Liao's quite the celebrity now

532
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:01,200
We've got a lot on our plate

533
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:03,400
He handles every last detail himself

534
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:04,040
Thanks for your hard work

535
00:28:04,760 --> 00:28:05,480
It's my duty

536
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:06,320
Not bad at all

537
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:07,520
You're really popular these days

538
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:09,880
I even followed you and liked your posts.

539
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:12,080
Thank you, Secretary Chen

540
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:13,200
Follow Old Liao

541
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,800
He'll show you a thing or two

542
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:16,440
He'll show you a thing or two

543
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:17,640
Thanks, thanks, thanks

544
00:28:18,360 --> 00:28:18,760
Thanks a lot

545
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:20,720
Enough of that

546
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,080
Hurry up and ask

547
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:23,840
When is Xuan Yan and their team

548
00:28:23,840 --> 00:28:24,680
going to arrive?

549
00:28:26,320 --> 00:28:27,560
They keep calling to rush us

550
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:28,720
Don't worry, you two

551
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,000
Go ask, go ask

552
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:34,000
Is this Xuan Yan?

553
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:35,200
Hello

554
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:35,840
Have you arrived yet?

555
00:28:36,760 --> 00:28:38,200
What loan? Wrong number

556
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:41,720
They're here, they're here!

557
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,200
My glasses

558
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:46,680
Excuse me, excuse me, coming through

559
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:56,800
Come on, come on, come on!

560
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:15,680
Distinguished guests, fellow townsfolk,

561
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:16,640
hello, everyone.

562
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:17,760
Peach Blossom Pond

563
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:20,600
welcomes you to the Dragon Boat Race.

564
00:29:20,600 --> 00:29:21,680
We're delighted to have you here.

565
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:30,040
Dragon boats race every year, but this year is different.

566
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:32,600
Today, Peach Blossom Town's Xuan paper firms

567
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:35,480
will compete with an unprecedented

568
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,320
paper dragon boat.

569
00:29:36,320 --> 00:29:39,840
Preserving Xuan paper and human heritage.

570
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:41,480
The race is about to begin.

571
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:44,880
Please welcome Jing County Party Secretary Chen Yunqing

572
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:47,080
to deliver the opening address.

573
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:58,800
Distinguished guests, competitors,

574
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:01,480
fellow townsfolk, hello everyone.

575
00:30:04,040 --> 00:30:05,360
Here at Peach Blossom Pond today,

576
00:30:06,120 --> 00:30:08,800
the drums stir a thousand years of poetry.

577
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:10,240
The chairman wants me and Yuqing

578
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:12,320
to bring the contract to Shenzhen to meet him.

579
00:30:13,520 --> 00:30:15,320
I have to catch a flight in an hour.

580
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:17,480
If you really don't want to sign it,

581
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:18,920
then don't sign it.

582
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:22,200
A warm welcome to friends from all corners.

583
00:30:23,040 --> 00:30:26,160
Hearty congratulations on this competition.

584
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:28,520
And to everyone who carries on the dragon boat spirit,

585
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:29,760
every hard-working soul among you,

586
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:30,800
I offer my deepest respect.

587
00:30:30,800 --> 00:30:31,760
President Xin.

588
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:33,760
Get out.

589
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:37,640
Peach Blossom Pond, at this moment,

590
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:40,000
echoes Li Bai's poem about Wang Lun,

591
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:40,920
a thousand-year echo,

592
00:30:41,280 --> 00:30:43,880
and the ten miles of blossoms and countless inns

593
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,320
that welcome the world in a modern sequel.

594
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:50,040
Wang Lun invited Li Bai with poetry and wine.

595
00:30:50,240 --> 00:30:53,080
Today, with racing dragon boats

596
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,760
and the beauty of Xuan paper on display,

597
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:58,240
we invite friends from everywhere to these waters,

598
00:30:58,240 --> 00:31:01,680
to join a feast blending past and present.

599
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,520
Now, let us welcome

600
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:05,320
Peach Blossom Town Party Secretary,

601
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:07,760
Secretary Peng, to declare the race open.

602
00:31:14,120 --> 00:31:15,200
I won't say much more.

603
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:16,800
I now declare

604
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:20,440
that the 12th Dragon Boat Race

605
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:21,560
is now open.

606
00:31:21,560 --> 00:31:22,600
Great, great.

607
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:23,000
Come on!

608
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:24,640
Go for it!

609
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:25,600
Everyone, go!

610
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:02,840
All teams, get ready!

611
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:05,560
On your marks!

612
00:32:11,120 --> 00:32:16,520
Go, go, go!

613
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,080
Come on! Come on!

614
00:32:49,560 --> 00:32:54,920
Come on! Come on! Come on!

615
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:22,560
The truth is, to Peach Blossom Town,

616
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:24,680
we're both outsiders.

617
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:27,160
If there's a piece of the pie to grab,

618
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,680
then we stick around a few more years.

619
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:31,840
If not, we just turn and walk away.

620
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:34,000
We came here to make some money, that's all.

621
00:33:34,360 --> 00:33:36,160
You've been around the block, after all.

622
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,480
Don't play the fool like Xuan Yan.

623
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:40,400
You've got to look ahead.

624
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:49,360
Come on, come on, come on!

625
00:34:05,360 --> 00:34:06,160
Auntie

626
00:34:08,719 --> 00:34:09,520
Xiao Xing

627
00:34:10,719 --> 00:34:11,760
What brings you here?

628
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:12,960
Come give Auntie a hug

629
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:16,960
Let me guess

630
00:34:18,239 --> 00:34:19,560
Your dad sent you here

631
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:22,080
This time I didn't take any money from my dad

632
00:34:22,080 --> 00:34:23,639
I came to see you all on my own

633
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:25,040
It's too noisy in here

634
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:26,760
Let's go outside to talk

635
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:28,840
Auntie

636
00:34:29,679 --> 00:34:31,040
My dad said

637
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:34,320
Uncle Xuan Yan and the others won't be your friends anymore

638
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:36,159
And you didn't go to the Dragon Boat Race

639
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:42,000
I figured you'd be really lonely all by yourself

640
00:34:42,159 --> 00:34:43,480
So I wanted to come keep you company

641
00:34:45,159 --> 00:34:46,679
You really are such a good kid

642
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,159
Let Auntie tell you something

643
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:50,840
It's not their fault, it's Auntie's fault.

644
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:54,239
Auntie did something very wrong.

645
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:56,199
I know how it feels to be alone.

646
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:58,240
Being lonely is really hard.

647
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:00,960
You're absolutely right.

648
00:35:01,600 --> 00:35:04,880
Auntie is having a really hard day today.

649
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:08,040
They're about to lose, look at that

650
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:10,360
It's fine, taking part is what counts

651
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:10,920
Right

652
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:11,400
Isn't it?

653
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:13,000
As long as you take part, that's good enough

654
00:35:13,160 --> 00:35:14,200
The way I see it

655
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,560
They've already won

656
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:18,480
They deserve a Best Contribution Award.

657
00:35:18,600 --> 00:35:20,520
Just look at how the crowd is reacting

658
00:35:20,520 --> 00:35:21,560
So enthusiastic

659
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:23,080
If they don't give them an award

660
00:35:23,240 --> 00:35:24,280
The audience just won't have it

661
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:24,800
Right

662
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:27,880
Go, go, go!

663
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:31,400
Not the fastest, just the coolest

664
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:34,360
Xuan paper dragon boat, one of a kind!

665
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,120
Xiao Xing

666
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,640
Can I ask you a question?

667
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,680
Go ahead.

668
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:07,680
If your teacher told you to lie

669
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,640
and bully your best classmate,

670
00:36:10,120 --> 00:36:11,240
and if you refused,

671
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:12,640
the teacher would kick you out of school.

672
00:36:12,960 --> 00:36:13,920
Would you do it?

673
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:14,960
Of course not.

674
00:36:15,120 --> 00:36:15,960
Why not?

675
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:16,920
If I were made

676
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:19,120
to hurt my classmate for no reason,

677
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:21,160
I'd feel awful inside.

678
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,520
I wouldn't like that.

679
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:25,240
But then you couldn't go to school.

680
00:36:25,240 --> 00:36:27,120
So if the school won't let me stay,

681
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,320
I'll just wander the world.

682
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,240
I can go wherever I want to go

683
00:36:30,240 --> 00:36:31,640
and live the life I want.

684
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:33,480
I'll be thrifty with food and everything.

685
00:36:35,600 --> 00:36:36,400
Xiao Xing,

686
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:39,680
you've always been such a brave kid.

687
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:41,960
I want to tell you,

688
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:45,320
don't wrong yourself or make yourself sad.

689
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:47,000
I can take you wandering with me.

690
00:36:54,040 --> 00:36:55,160
Thank you, Xiao Xing.

691
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,640
Mr. Xuan

692
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:08,800
Congratulations!

693
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,080
Congratulations to your team.

694
00:37:10,080 --> 00:37:11,000
Thank you, Secretary Peng.

695
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:13,200
Thank you.

696
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:13,880
Thank you.

697
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:16,040
One of a kind!

698
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:26,320
We look the coolest!

699
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:27,800
One more shot, one more shot!

700
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,120
Mr. Liao, Mr. Liao, here.

701
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,200
Thank you, thank you.

702
00:37:31,040 --> 00:37:32,760
Three, two, one.

703
00:37:36,160 --> 00:37:38,160
Let's record a video, shout a slogan.

704
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,480
Okay.

705
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:44,960
Not the fastest, but the coolest!

706
00:37:45,160 --> 00:37:47,080
Xuan paper dragon boat!

707
00:37:47,160 --> 00:37:49,400
One of a kind!

708
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:51,160
What are you doing?

709
00:37:51,160 --> 00:37:51,960
So how was it?

710
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,240
Pretty great, wasn't it?

711
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:56,000
Did you forget?

712
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:58,000
We still have a bet, you know.

713
00:37:58,640 --> 00:37:59,360
Seriously?

714
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:01,520
You still want me to apologize now?

715
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:02,560
So petty.

716
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:04,960
Of course not.

717
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:07,040
It's time to come home for dinner, right?

718
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:18,760
Can you do it?

719
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:21,440
Yeah.

720
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:23,520
Time to go home for dinner!

721
00:38:24,160 --> 00:38:24,840
Hey, Xuan Yan.

722
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:25,840
Xuan Yan, Xuan Yan, Xuan Yan.

723
00:38:28,560 --> 00:38:29,560
One of a kind.

724
00:38:29,640 --> 00:38:30,320
Old Xuan.

725
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:35,280
Xuan Yan.

726
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,040
Uncle Xuan Yan.

727
00:38:38,640 --> 00:38:39,240
Put me down!

728
00:38:39,240 --> 00:38:39,960
Uncle Xuan Yan.

729
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:43,440
Xiao Xing.

730
00:38:43,640 --> 00:38:44,120
Xiao Xing.

731
00:38:45,040 --> 00:38:46,480
Xiao Xing, your dad's over there.

732
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:49,080
Auntie Xin Ran told me to give you this.

733
00:38:50,160 --> 00:38:50,960
Xin Ran.

734
00:39:02,640 --> 00:39:03,600
There's a letter too.

735
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,240
It's for me.

736
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,080
Xin Ran.

737
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,000
Go ahead.

738
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,360
There's one crucial thing

739
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:19,240
I need to remind you of.

740
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:21,920
You must go to a notary for preservation of evidence.

741
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:24,360
The contract between Dayazhai and Xuan Yan

742
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,960
carries some evidentiary value as well.

743
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:41,160
Come on

744
00:39:41,160 --> 00:39:43,840
Watch me, one, two, one, two, three

745
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:47,640
Excuse me, excuse me, sorry

746
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:49,560
Sorry, coming through, excuse me

747
00:39:50,040 --> 00:39:52,440
Everyone, everyone, everyone

748
00:39:52,480 --> 00:39:56,160
Someone gave me crucial evidence.

749
00:39:56,600 --> 00:39:58,280
Xuan Bao'er and Paper Fairy!

750
00:39:58,520 --> 00:39:59,800
We have a chance to win them back

751
00:40:00,680 --> 00:40:01,680
Win them back

752
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:09,320
We have hope now

753
00:40:10,560 --> 00:40:11,520
There's hope

754
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:16,920
Where's Aunt Xin Ran?

755
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:19,600
She said she'd come back once she was done

756
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:23,080
I don't think she's coming back

757
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:23,800
No way

758
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:26,000
She said she'd go wandering with me

759
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:27,080
Wandering

760
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:33,680
This is her letter

761
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:39,640
Xuan Yan, may this letter reach you as I would

762
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:42,840
This USB has my talks with the Chairman

763
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:45,000
about the Xuan Bao'er you designed,

764
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:46,040
held on several occasions

765
00:40:46,680 --> 00:40:48,640
All of it took place

766
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:51,560
before they squatted your copyright and patent.

767
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:53,640
Guided by my lawyer friend,

768
00:40:53,640 --> 00:40:55,480
the evidence has been notarized

769
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:57,960
and holds full legal validity

770
00:40:58,560 --> 00:40:59,520
If necessary,

771
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:01,560
I can testify in court as a witness

772
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,320
I'm sorry, my friend

773
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:07,480
Because I lacked the courage

774
00:41:07,960 --> 00:41:10,520
to stand up for justice in time,

775
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,800
you and your friends in Peach Blossom Town

776
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:13,960
have suffered because of it

777
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:18,120
I don't expect you to forgive immediately

778
00:41:18,120 --> 00:41:19,880
this coward who came too late.

779
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:21,720
I only hope that, fighting for justice,

780
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:24,120
charging through the darkness before dawn,

781
00:41:24,520 --> 00:41:27,560
may this evidence light your way.

782
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:30,480
Forever owing you an apology,

783
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:31,880
Xin Ran

784
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,200
President Xin

785
00:41:46,120 --> 00:41:46,960
President Xin

786
00:41:48,240 --> 00:41:49,160
What are you doing here?

787
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,440
We came looking for you.

788
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:54,920
Leaving without a word isn't your style, President Xin.

789
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:59,720
Stop calling me President Xin.

790
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,360
Just call me Xin Ran.

791
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:04,320
Xin Ran.

792
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:08,720
Have you thought about joining our factory?

793
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:11,200
Xiao Min.

794
00:42:11,280 --> 00:42:12,760
I've already told you.

795
00:42:13,520 --> 00:42:14,880
I really can't do it.

796
00:42:15,680 --> 00:42:16,880
If not the factory, that's fine too.

797
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:21,520
Then apply to be general manager at our Cooperative.

798
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,800
The pay and benefits are very generous.

799
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:27,840
Most importantly, it's close to home.

800
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:29,360
Right?

801
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,360
What do you mean by that?

802
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:34,800
Auntie Xin, please don't go, okay?

803
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,320
I don't want you to leave.

804
00:42:37,640 --> 00:42:38,440
Xiao Xing.

805
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,800
Auntie doesn't want to leave you either.

806
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:43,800
Auntie will call you often from now on.

807
00:42:43,800 --> 00:42:44,560
Okay?

808
00:42:46,080 --> 00:42:46,880
Xin Ran.

809
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:51,720
Please stay.

810
00:42:52,640 --> 00:42:54,480
That's what Xiao Xing and I truly feel.

811
00:42:55,640 --> 00:42:56,640
No matter where you are,

812
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:58,800
you can realize your life's worth.
